&lt;p&gt;Taking a page (or really, an …&lt;/p&gt;</summary><category term="new year"></category><category term="blog"></category></entry><entry><title>Game-ify Your Raspberry Pi</title><link href="https://magsol.github.io/blog/2017/01/06/gameify-your-raspberry-pi/" rel="alternate"></link><published>2017-01-06T18:47:37-05:00</published><updated>2017-01-06T18:47:37-05:00</updated><author><name>Shannon Quinn</name></author><id>tag:magsol.github.io,2017-01-06:blog/2017/01/06/gameify-your-raspberry-pi/</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="/images/rpi/raspberrypi3.jpg"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
